== Testing Pandoc Template Syntax ==

-- Basic interpolation --
Title: $title$

-- Variable with pipe --
Title uppercase: $title/uppercase$

-- Variable with separator (array iteration shorthand) --
Items: $items[, ]$

-- Variable with pipe AND separator --
Tags: $tags/uppercase[; ]$

-- For loop with sep --
Authors:
$for(author)$
  - $author.name$ <$author.email$>
$sep$
$endfor$

-- Partial without variable --
$author-card()$

-- Partial with variable (iterates over array) --
$author:author-card()$

-- Partial with separator --
$author:author-card()[---]$

-- Partial with pipe (after separator) --
$author:author-card()[---]/chomp$

-- Metadata pairs pipe --
Metadata:
$for(metadata/pairs)$
  $it.key$: $it.value$
$endfor$

-- Conditional --
$if(title)$
Has title: $title$
$else$
No title
$endif$

-- Nesting directive --
Description: $^$$title$ is a test document
             with multiple lines of content.

== End of Template ==
